{"tid":1380691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解構黑警新款鎮壓裝備 催淚彈橡膠彈已升級","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T06:02:34.000Z","uid":228656,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"834894a2ef55b54c8f75a6cd0cea2823e261d85d","tid":1380691,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"【解構黑警新款鎮壓裝備 催淚彈橡膠彈已升級】<br />\n&mdash;&mdash; 到底昨日我地俾乜野子彈射中？<br />\n<br />\n全文<br />\n<br />\n//以上所有武器都無論點轉都有一個共通點，#就係全部鎮壓武器都係美國🇺🇸公司出品。喺香港警察多次濫用暴力鎮壓示威嘅情況下，任何國家都唔應該容許自己國家有公司售賣武器俾香港黑警。<br />\n<br />\n以前話「香港警察 知法犯法」，今日最準確既說法應該係「香港警察 意圖謀殺」，奉勸美國作為「民主大國」唔該停止成為幫兇，唔好再賣武器俾香港警察，請傚法英國政府既做法，停止出口人群管制裝備比香港警察！<br />\n<br />\n【白官聯署：美國應該停止出口人群管制裝備予香港警察】<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67RPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=6bc733a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses</a><br />\n<br />\n（再次感謝幾位 #眾志研究員，無佢地通宵砌到朝早七點，大家唔會未到中午就已經見到曬新子彈新武器既何等痴線）//<br />\n<br />\n大家快啲幫手簽咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70497c5b1c48eb12edbe9c8e155b096affdb1271","tid":1380691,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:33:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"031c21c82df9fb1d999c0ad199e4d351e990d0f5","tid":1380691,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:33:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d2a6562f35d5a5f89921ff3d23959f214b804b4d","tid":1380691,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05: